---
title: Press
layout: page
---
%ul.article-list
  - blog.articles.each do |article|
    %li.article-list-item
      %article
        %h2.article-title
          = link_to article.title, article
        %h4.article-date
          %time= article.date.strftime('%b %e %Y')
        -# = article.summary
        - if article.data.gallery?
          = image_tag(article.data.gallery.first)
